sect1.para:
To view properties of a PGP key:




		Select the PGP key 
		from the main window,





		Double click on it or choose Properties 
		from the toolbar,





		Select the Details tab.

    	    To view properties of a SSH key:




				Select the Secure Shell key 
				from the main window,





				Double click on it or choose Properties 
				from the toolbar,





				Select the Details tab.
